task.summary: Some repairs and improvements due to recent IDC-Common merge
Utility to generate the 'filters' schema based on 'attributes' in the current DB.
Add manifest API and tests. Extended gen_filters_json.py to generate additional schemas.
Some changes to the data returned by the /attributes API

Fixed schema validation: add "additionProperties": True to filters schema. Had to post process json generation because it output "true" instead of "True". Fix some error checking to return more specific error codes. Add a simple test to check that schema validation is working.
Eliminated some options from /cohorts/{cohort_id}. Working on /collections API.
Multiple fixes, mostly for compatibility with new IDC version in the model.
Add 'None' option to cohort object hierarchy return.
